rows.label: tlk45310111_03_msg0001
rows.name:
That was a terrible ordeal
back there... I'm just glad
we got out of it in one piece.

rows.label: tlk45310111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
D'you think Chairman Bahn
didn't know those people
were members of Iira?

rows.label: tlk45310111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I hope he'll investigate his
clients more closely before
taking on jobs in future...

rows.label: tlk45310111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Those guys weren't normal,
I tell you. It's a miracle
that we escaped alive!
